{"tid":1950903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田豪宅玖瓏山20歲女子確診　未即時送院令住戶人心惶惶","createTime":"2020-03-30T15:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T14:59:14.000Z","uid":209657,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0778e864be1c53af5429a1ab203d144a56a9e8ef","tid":1950903,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4240589/org/cd660315374ae17e1ea0daaa19151332.jpg/3ZLJpkpl2HK59SqI9IBAnFNNIo2W2Dg6KTizcSk4s3E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4240589%2Forg%2Fcd660315374ae17e1ea0daaa19151332.jpg%2F3ZLJpkpl2HK59SqI9IBAnFNNIo2W2Dg6KTizcSk4s3E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a0a56259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞生署「2019冠狀病毒病」網站資料顯示，玖瓏山目前已有2宗外地輸入的確診個案，其中第204宗的43歲女患者是3月19日確診，她居於月瓏閣第3座，已獲安排入院；而558宗確診個案居於傲瓏閣第3座，該名20歲女生在3月23日病發，至3月28日確診。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，有人於網上討論區透露，該女生從外國返港，衞生署其後將患者的4名家人送往檢疫中心隔離，惟患者未有即時送院。而截至3月30日晚上8時50分，衞生署網站資料顯示20歲女患者仍是「待入院」狀態。"},{"pid":"1dd60add7377130570411162377a1e57f9053367","tid":1950903,"uid":209657,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"20歲 玖瓏山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0703114d25fa27c07f17211a30e55af1fab2b82c","tid":1950903,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"Rich"},{"pid":"7369e90019f3700d08e613a95cefe1c8dee85bc0","tid":1950903,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"肺花都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10f8b729bfc60a401bab942f66a1802fc62b68d","tid":1950903,"uid":94982,"like":1